Our square is mainly devoted to agricultural purposes,dairy farming interspersed with arable crops. {Karen}at our school lives on a typical farm.Here is her day .
My mum and dad do all the work out side. My brother and I do some jobs in doors. It is a 24 hour job.In the summer we are busy getting the hay in. In winter we are busy getting the snow off the road,for the milk lorry to come and get the milk. Life on the farm can be fun and interesting but sometimes it is boring. The name of our farm is{Folly Farm.
